## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **cenobamate Xcopri 2019** = dual GABA-A allosteric + Na channel inactivation — focal refractory. 2 mechanism in 1 molecule = next-gen AED. quantum-VQE 의 GABA-A α-subunit selectivity refinement 가 직접 fit.
2. **ganaxolone Ztalmy 2022** = first FDA CDKL5 deficiency disorder — neurosteroid GABA-A allosteric (allopregnanolone analogue). pediatric rare epilepsy precision 첫 사례.
3. **fenfluramine Fintepla 2020** = Dravet syndrome — 1997 phen-fen cardiac valvulopathy 철수 후 23년 만에 새 적응증 재진입. risk 관리 REMS.
4. **cannabidiol Epidiolex 2018** = first plant-derived cannabinoid FDA — Dravet + LGS + TSC. CB1/CB2 외 multi-target (TRPV1 + GPR55 + adenosine + 5-HT1A).
5. **brivaracetam + perampanel + lacosamide 2008-2016** = SV2A + AMPA + slow Na channel = AED 표적 다양화 paradigm shift. classical Na/GABA 외.
6. **everolimus Afinitor 2018 TSC-related epilepsy** = mTOR pathway = oncology 약물 (RCC + breast 등) 의 epilepsy repurpose. cross-link `.roadmap.disease_pediatric_rare` TSC.
7. **diazepam (Valtoco 2020) + midazolam (Nayzilam 2019) nasal** = acute seizure cluster + status epilepticus prehospital — IM/IV 외 nasal 경로 = patient/caregiver 자가투여.
8. **vigabatrin Sabril 2009 + felbamate Felbatol 1993** = irreversible GABA-T (시야 위험) + NMDA glycine (재생불량성빈혈 위험) — 효과 강력 but safety REMS 강제.
9. **valproate teratogenicity Holmes 2008 + APR 2024** = fetal valproate syndrome counsel. 임신 가능 여성 처방 패러다임 변화. lamotrigine + levetiracetam preferred.
10. **DBS anterior thalamus 2018 + RNS 2013** = device — closed-loop neurostimulation. drug refractory 30% 의 마지막 옵션. wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음 — quantum-only in-silico, epilepsy 임상 의미 한정.

